WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Planning a mountain hike requires careful mathematics!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
We calculate distances, estimate walking times, and plan rest stops.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Safety depends on accurate measurements and calculations.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Weather, terrain, and fitness all affect our mathematical planning.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's use maths to plan safe mountain adventures!